{{Infobox book | name = The Globalization of World Politics: An Introduction to International Relations (6th ed) | title_orig = | translator = | image = The Globalization of World Politics.jpg | caption = | editors = Patricia Owens, John Baylis, Steve Smith | illustrator = | cover_artist = | country = | language = English | series = | subject = | genre = Nonfiction | publisher = Oxford University Press, USA | release_date = 12 December 2013 | english_release_date = | media_type = Paperback, Hardback | pages = 648 | isbn = 978-0-19-965617-2 | dewey= 327 22 | congress= JZ1242 .G58 2008 | oclc= 174500731 | preceded_by = | followed_by = }}
'''''The Globalization of World Politics: An Introduction to International Relations''''' is a book by John Baylis, Patricia Owens, and [[Steve Smith (academic)|Steve Smith]].
